    <title as="introduced" type="short">Montgomery GI Bill Improvements Act of 2001</title>
    <title as="introduced" type="official">To amend title 38, United States Code, to improve benefits under the Montgomery GI Bill by establishing an enhanced educational assistance program, by increasing the amount of basic educational assistance, by repealing the requirement for reduction in pay for participation in the program, by authorizing the Secretary of Veterans Affairs to make accelerated payments of basic educational assistance, and for other purposes.</title>
